      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for the daily grind? This car is a solid, honest performer that still has plenty of life left in it! While it shows some expected wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a dependable choice for anyone prioritizing value and utility. It\u2019s a great opportunity to get behind the wheel of a functional vehicle at a price that makes sense!",
